>Description:
I'd like to be able to run only the tests in a file from DrRacket. I know that the run button runs the tests and the fild, but it would be nice to do only tests.
>How-To-Repeat:
>Fix:
>Audit-Trail:
State changed from "open" to "closed" by jay at Fri, 17 May 2013 17:16:15 -0400
Reason>>> Go to the Language Details menu by going to "Choose a 
language" and then "Show Details" on "The Racket Language". 
The option "Submodules to Run" gives you a way to check off 
which you want and do not want to run.

